def has_stovefan(stove:item):
    # Determine if the stove has a stovefan
    symbol has_stovefan=exists stovefan:item: is_stovefan(stovefan) and close(stove, stovefan)
    return has_stovefan

behavior boil_pot_on_stove(pot:item, stove:item):
    body:
        achieve on(pot, stove)
        # Ensure that the pot is placed on the stove

        if has_stovefan(stove):
            bind stovefan: item where:
                is_stovefan(stovefan) and close(stove, stovefan)
            achieve_once is_on(stovefan)
            # If the stove has a stovefan, turn it on

        achieve is_on(stove)
        # Turn on the stove to boil the vegetables

behavior __goal__():

        bind pot: item where:
            is_pot(pot) and not visited(pot)
        # Select a pot that has not been visited

        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove)
        # Select the stove

        boil_pot_on_stove(pot, stove)
